# LogBurstMatrix - Log Frequency & Spike Analyzer

LogBurstMatrix lets you visualize dense logging patterns and catch burst anomalies across your infrastructure.

## Features
- Pattern clustering  
- Timestamp segmentation  
- CLI interface  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_LogBurstMatrix.git
cd 37_LogBurstMatrix
python analyze.py
